== About me
I am a final year undergraduate in the Department of Electrical and Computer Engineering at The University of Texas at Austin. 
#I am very fortunate to be advised by [https://sites.utexas.edu/mokhtari/ Prof. Aryan Mokhtari], #[https://vita-group.github.io/group.html/ Prof. Atlas Wang], and [https://sites.google.com/view/#sanjay-shakkottai/home/ Prof. Sanjay Shakkottai], as well as PhD students [https://#peihaowang.github.io/ Peihao Wang] and [https://liamgcollins.github.io/ Liam Collins].

== Research
I am interested in the Foundations of Machine Learning, especially in the following topics: 
- Federated Learning
- Representation Learning
- Sparsity in Machine Learning

